# Physics M³ Workspace

Computational mechanics workspace for multi-scale (M³) analysis.
Covers material characterization, FEM, CFD, topology optimization,
experimental validation, and VVV certification.

## Install
```bash
pip install -e .
```

## Run
```bash
physics-m3 demo
```

## Test
```bash
python -m pytest tests/ -v
```
